data.description: Welcome to 7570 Tatum Woods Dr, Cumming, GA 30028! This recently updated home offers modern living at its finest. Step inside to discover luxury vinyl plank flooring adorning most of the home, providing both durability and elegance. The kitchen boasts updated countertops and appliances, creating a chef's haven for culinary delights.    Experience the warmth of fresh paint throughout the home, enhancing the ambiance and creating a welcoming atmosphere. With spacious living areas and an open floor plan, this home is perfect for both entertaining guests and everyday living.    Located in the vibrant community of Cumming, GA, this residence offers convenience to local amenities, schools, and parks. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautifully updated home yours!
